GET /v1/version


Locked architectural decisions
/version is an operational endpoint used to identify the running service version.
It is independent of the Execution Trust architecture and does not expose any Business Transactions or trust artifacts.
It reports deployment metadata only, including:
Service version
API version
Build timestamp
Git commit (if available)
Deployment environment
The endpoint is intended for diagnostics, deployment verification, support, and operational tooling, and has no effect on business state or the Execution Trust Record.

